<header>
<div id="instruction">
	Read the writing task on the left and answer the questions on the right. In some cases, there is more than one correct answer.
	</div>
</header>
	
<section id="body">
<ol id="splitquestionList">

	<li>Who do you have to write to?
	<list class="answerList">
	<li><g id="t1">a stranger</g></li>
	<li><g id="t2">a close friend</g></li>
	<li><g id="t3">a penfriend</g></li>
	<li><g id="t4">a relative</g></li>
	<li><g id="t5">a colleague</g></li>
	</list></li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What style of letter should you write?
	<list class="answerList">
	<li><g id="t6">formal</g></li>
	<li><g id="t7">informal</g></li>
	</list></li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>What do you have to do in this letter?
	<list class="answerList">
	<li><g id="t8">A.  give advice</g></li>
	<li><g id="t9">B.  make arrangements</g></li>
	<li><g id="t10">C.  request information</g></li>
	<li><g id="t11">D.  explain a situation</g></li>
	<li><g id="t12">E.  make a complaint</g></li>
	</list></li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>How many points do you have to cover inthis letter?
	<list class="answerList">
	<li><g id="t13">A.  one</g></li>
	<li><g id="t14">B.  two</g></li>
	<li><g id="t15">C.  three</g></li>
	<li><g id="t16">D.  four</g></li>
	<li><g id="t17">E.  five</g></li>
	</list></li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>

	<li>Which of the following should you discussin this letter?
	<list class="answerList">
	<li><g id="t18">A.  the way the lessons are taught</g></li>
	<li><g id="t19">B.  the nationality of the teacher</g></li>
	<li><g id="t20">C.  the size of the classrooms</g></li>
	<li><g id="t21">D.  the maximum number of students per class</g></li>
	<li><g id="t22">E.  the intensity of the course</g></li>
	</list></li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>

	</ol>
	
